author: Xbox
description:
Before a sequel can be great, it must first be tested. Repeatedly, Infront of a group of complete strangers. 
 
This is The Outer Worlds 2 Focus Group – where the “Head of Sequels” and his panel of volunteers bravely explore the boundaries of personal space, T-shirt cannons, and the inappropriate use of gift cards. 
 
Some call it research. We call it Big Sequel Energy. 
 
The Outer Worlds 2 launches October 29th. Pre-Order now and play on October 24 if you buy the Premium Edition.
 
https://www.xbox.com/games/the-outer-worlds-2

The Outer Worlds 2 is the eagerly-awaited sequel to the award-winning first-person sci-fi RPG from Obsidian Entertainment (just look at the exciting number of dashes in this sentence!). Time to clear your calendar – get ready for an action-packed adventure with a new crew, new weapons, and new enemies in a new colony! So much newness!

author: Xbox
description:
Beneath will launch on Xbox Series X|S October 28th.

Beneath is a Lovecraft-inspired survival FPS built by two brothers. Scarce ammo, merciless enemies and a sense of the unknown combine in a 10+ hour, story-driven single player campaign, built for both veteran gamers and those seeking an old school experience.

Seasoned diver Noah Quinn’s routine expedition plunges him into chaos, trapping him in the depths of the ocean, where an ancient evil lurks. As supplies dwindle and nightmarish creatures close in, Noah must confront horrifying mutations and unravel a sinister conspiracy that threatens humanity itself. With his daughter’s life hanging in the balance, Noah is pushed to his limits in a desperate race against time. Can he uncover the truth and stop an ancient horror from surfacing, or will the abyss consume them all?
